title: Consumer tech company udChalo to cater to housing demand from armed forces - Economic Times
content: Consumer tech company udChalo to cater to housing demand from armed forces  Economic Times
description: udChalo plans to enter markets like Chandigarh, NCR Delhi, Bengaluru and Jaipur. The brand is in conversation with reputed developers in these cities which will further ensure better buying options and a hassle-free home buying journey for its consumer base.
